=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
תּהוּ / tôhû / to'-hoo
=== Etymology ===

From an unused root meaning to lie waste; 
=== Noun ===
a desolation (of surface), that is, desert; figuratively a worthless thing; adverbially in vain: - [[confusion]], empty place, without form, nothing, (thing of) nought, [[vain]], vanity, [[waste]], [[wilderness]].